strings: <voice_0x01001D0F><se_high>Princess Medea: Isn't it wonderful that Cash and Carrie both managed to complete the trial?
<voice_0x01001D10><se_high>Princess Medea: Now they can work together to carry on their father's business.

<voice_0x01001D11><se_high>Princess Medea: They're actually very close, aren't they <endash>
beneath all the bickering, I mean.

<voice_0x01001D12><se_high>Princess Medea: We used to fight, too, do you remember?
When we were little.
<voice_0x01001D13><se_high>Princess Medea: I always thought of you as my older brother...
<voice_0x01001D14><se_high>Princess Medea: But now I see you more as...a man.
<voice_0x01001D15><se_high>Princess Medea: I, I mean, never mind, forget I said anything. Goodnight.
